   reimplementations of, logic in llccd/TermWrap:

     - crates/patcher/src/pattern.rs  (`pattenMatch` 4-byte-aligned scan)
     - crates/patcher/src/pe.rs       (PE base/header adjustment logic)
     - crates/termwrap-dll/**         (patch set, x64 xref resolution,
         x86 prologue-scan resolution)
     - crates/offset-finder/src/xref_x86.rs  (x86 branch-follower
         stride matches TermWrap)

