   `SvchostPushServiceGlobals`) is the interface rdprrap implements for
   drop-in compatibility with consumers of the original wrapper; the
   interface itself is the Windows TermService ABI, not the TermWrap
   project's copyrighted material, but attribution is acknowledged here
   out of respect for the upstream work.


